The complete SLA timeline (i.e. all START, STOP events for an SLE) is stored as a document field and is used to determine the last complete cycle during report rendering.

h3. Issue Summary

Search request type with multibyte keyword in customer portal doesn't return any results
h3. Environment
 - Jira Service Desk 4.1.0
 - (!) Not to be reproduced in Jira Service Desk 4.0.2, 4.2.1

h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Create new request type which is called "テスト"
 # Input a keyword "テスト" in customer portal search field

h3. Expected Results

The request type should be suggested.
h3. Actual Results

Doen't return any request type with keyword "テスト".

!Screen Shot 2019-05-29 at 11.35.33.png|thumbnail!

!Screen Shot 2019-05-29 at 11.35.47.png|thumbnail!
h3. Notes

Multibyte text "テスト" encoded 2 times.
 - {{<BASE_URL>/rest/servicedesk/search/1/search/request-type?query=%25E3%2583%2586%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2583%2588&resultLimit=5&serviceDeskId=1&_=1559096535526}}
{code:java}
{
	requestTypes: [ ]
}
{code}

When decode the query, return proper results.
 - {{<BASE_URL>/rest/servicedesk/search/1/search/request-type?query=%E3%83%86%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88&resultLimit=5&serviceDeskId=1&_=1559097269350}}
{code:java}
{
	requestTypes: [
		{
			id: 17,
			cvId: 1,
			icon: 10638,
			issueType: 10001,
			name: "テスト",
			portalName: "IT Service Desk",
			description: "Japanese",
			searchScore: 0
		}
	]
}
{code}

"Search for an article" has same issue.
 - {{<BASE_URL>/rest/servicedesk/knowledgebase/latest/articles/search?project=ISD&query=%25E3%2583%2586%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2583%2588&_=1559116663620}}
{code:java}
{
	results: [ ],
	total: 0,
	pageNumber: 1,
	resultsPerPage: 3
}
{code}

 - {{<BASE_URL>/rest/servicedesk/knowledgebase/latest/articles/search?project=ISD&query=%E3%83%86%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88&_=1559116663620}}
{code:java}
{
	results: [
		{
			id: "65622",
			title: "@@@hl@@@テスト@@@endhl@@@３",
			url: "/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=65622&src=search",
			appLinkUrl: "http://confluence:8090",
			shareable: true,
			bodyTextHighlights: "て",
			portalName: "IT Service Desk",
			spaceKey: "ds",
			appLinkId: "ab9528d2-ba64-36d2-ad73-62624a5c7f9f"
		}
	],
	total: 1,
	pageNumber: 1,
	resultsPerPage: 3
}
{code}

h3. Workaround

Upgrade to latest version.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Service Desk Server*. Using *JIRA Service Desk Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSDCLOUD-1515].
  {panel}

Agents should have the ability to create a signature for their responses to Service Desk customers to prevent having to copy/paste or type out a signature for each response.

There may be a use case for the ability to set these signatures per agent per service desk, also.

